{"tid":1959063,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大巴拿又中肺炎。。。","createTime":"2020-04-05T06:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T08:58:48.000Z","uid":16320,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee44a07705f8b31aa5bc000ddaba154777b2d24","tid":1959063,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"測試陰轉返陽 迪巴拿「再確診」<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】祖雲達斯前鋒迪巴拿和女友Oriana Sabatini本以為已從新型冠狀病毒中痊癒，誰知在最新一次檢測後發現再次呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n迪巴拿（Paulo Dybala）和Oriana Sabatini早前感染了新型冠狀病毒，兩人於數天前宣佈已經再沒有出現病徵，不再需要自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n不過，Oriana最近透露，她跟迪巴拿原來仍然未康復：「我們在3月21日的檢測結果屬陽性，3天前再測試則是陰性，但做第3次檢測後發現又是陽性，即是說我仍然帶有新型冠狀病毒，我不知道為甚麼。」由於病毒的檢測結果反覆，Oriana呼籲大家有必要至少自我隔離2星期。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，迪巴拿早前已表示感覺好多了：「我一開始咳嗽得厲害，覺得人很疲憊，睡覺的時候覺得很冷。起初我沒有想過自己是甚麼情況，但同樣的症狀在其他兩名隊友身上也出現了，我是最後一個。」"},{"pid":"f9bb36146779344c9987c973c2e7292b45d1822f","tid":1959063,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入想點呀，放過bb啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3c58d87b4bf0c695adf7e58b9b75693c4e224d","tid":1959063,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30085f540685a8c667051f615cd8735c8f03b90","tid":1959063,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"根本冇得斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a54d610f38604b4451b3b05dfe1eb30262652b","tid":1959063,"uid":354329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"902b250f1d2a7be24ba6673c680647811ced7f67","tid":1959063,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":